g%20to%20fill%20this%20oversized%20canvas%20using%20my%20once%20pristine%20tubes%20of%20paint%2C%20now%20squished%20and%20dented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213caf8f8-7780-43c8-b201-1ff02af24c3d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20my%20teacher's%20gift%20meant%20to%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20from%20a%20different%20cultural%20background%2C%20sometimes%20people%20overlook%20what%20you%20have%20in%20common%3Cspan%3E.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20colleague%20asked%20me%20what%C2%A0my%20family%C2%A0does%20this%20time%20of%20year%20despite%20encouraging%20everyone%20else%20to%20share%20their%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristmas-traditions-alternatives-holiday-family-meaningful-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%20plans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Remarks%20like%20these%20single%20you%20out%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20not%20in%20the%20caring%20way%20of%20a%20teacher%20who%20pays%20you%20a%20genuine%20compliment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20one%20of%20a%20few%20kids%20in%20my%20fourth-grade%20class%20from%20an%20immigrant%20family%20and%20a%20single-parent%20household%2C%20everywhere%20I%20looked%2C%20there%20was%20someone%20whose%20life%20looked%20different%20from%20mine.%20But%20instead%20of%20assuming%20I%20didn't%20celebrate%20Christmas%2C%20which%20I%20did%2C%20my%20teacher%20just%20wanted%20me%20to%20feel%20included.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20generous%20gift%20showed%20me%20I%20had%20a%20talent%20worth%20buying%20and%20actually%20using%20quality%20art%20supplies.%20She%20even%20had%20my%20painting%20professionally%20framed%20like%20my%20mom%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20saw%20it%20once%20when%20we%20drove%20by%20her%20house%20in%20the%20sixth%20grade.%20It%20was%2C%20just%20as%20she%20said%2C%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20her%20living%20room%2C%20surrounded%20by%20custom%20matting