nk%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20for%20somebody%20that%20hates%20real%20estate%20but%20understands%20the%20tax%20benefits%20of%20real%20estate%20to%20get%20in%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-a-millionaire-couple-invests-their-money-etfs-meta-bitcoin-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eself-made%20millionaire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20founder%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbudgetdog.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBudgetdog%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20who%20built%20his%20wealth%20primarily%20investing%20in%20low-cost%20index%20funds%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246884175-e064-4a5c-be62-2b091570177b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20real-estate%20syndications%20work%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20real-estate%20syndication%20deals%2C%20a%20group%20of%20investors%20pools%20together%20their%20capital%20to%20purchase%20a%20single%20property%20managed%20by%20the%20syndicator.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20the%20investor%20contributes%20capital%2C%20their%20role%20in%20the%20deal%20becomes%20completely%20passive.%20The%20real-estate%20syndicator%20is%20responsible%20for%20finding%20the%20deal%2C%20executing%20the%20transaction%2C%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20delivering%20returns%20to%20the%20investors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20lose%20control%20from%20that%20aspect.%20You%20don't%20really%20have%20control%20over%20how%20that%20performs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schlagbaum%2C%20who%20said%20he%20invests%20in%20five%20multi-family%20syndications.%20But%20if%20you%20work%20with%20a%20syndicator%20with%20a%20good%20track%20record%20that%20you%20trust%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20essentially%20an%20index%20fund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20invests%20with%20a%20syndicator%20that%20specializes%20in%20multi-family%20properties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThey%20go%20in%2C%20upgrade%20the%20units%2C%20increase%20rent%20prices%20in%20a%20really%20high-demand%20area%20that's%20underpriced%2C%20own%20and%20operate%20that%20building%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20then%20typically%20sell%20it%20after%20a%20three-%20to%20five-year%20period%2C%20sometimes%20up%20to%20seven%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20don't%20do%20anything%20as%20an%20investor%3B%20you're%20just%20an%20equity%20partner.%20So%20you%20literally%20send%20some%20capital%20their%20way%20and%20hope%20they%20do%20their%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd65a874-a8ec-4be1-921d-57fec824ff4e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20good%20option%20for%20established%20investors%20looking%20for%20hands-off%20strategies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBI%20has%20spoken%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20established%20investors%20who%2C%20after%20building%20wealth%20by%20acquiring%20rental%20properties%2C%20are%20turning%20to%20syndication%20deals%20for%20a%20more%20passive%20experience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20hear%20that%20real-estate%20investing%20is%20passive%2C%20and%20that's%20certainly%20not%20been%20my%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-made-millionaire-shares-her-portfolio-how-she-invests-money-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eself-made%20millionaire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Tess%20Waresmith%2C%20who%20owns%20five%20units%20across%20three%20properties.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20think%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20way%20to%20invest%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20passive%20like%20investing%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20invested%20in%20her%20first%20syndication%20in%202023%20and%20likes%20that%20it%20opens%20th