20in%20one%20(MBB)%20basket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20interested%20in%20consulting%20are%20set%20on%20joining%20a%20prestigious%20firm%2C%20like%20an%20MBB%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20EY%2C%20PwC%2C%20KPMG%2C%20and%20Deloitte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20Management%20Consulted%20clients%20do%20land%20at%20those%20firms%2C%20Mian%20said%20it's%20important%20applicants%20keep%20their%20options%20open%2C%20and%20that%20there%20are%20often%20great%20opportunities%20at%20lesser%20known%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20literally%20hundreds%20of%20consulting%20firms%20out%20there%20doing%20amazing%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20pay%20just%20as%20well%20as%20the%20MBB%20or%20the%20Big%20Four%2C%20and%20nobody's%20ever%20heard%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMian%20noted%20that%20Management%20Consulted's%20salary%20report%2C%20which%20includes%20salary%20data%20from%20more%20than%20100%20firms%2C%20shows%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20lesser-known%20companies%20with%20high-paying%20starting%20salaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20generally%20advise%20clients%20to%20identify%20and%20focus%20on%20six%20to%20eight%20firms.%20The%20goal%20is%C2%A0for%20clients%20to%20have%20several%20offers%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20process%20that%20they%20can%20leverage%20against%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22163dec15-7234-4537-b54f-52ba7e263f7b%5C%22%3ETiming%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHiring%20in%20consulting%20works%20on%20pretty%20specific%20timelines%2C%20which%20vary%20depending%20on%20where%20the%20applicant%20is%20in%20their%20schooling%2C%20Mian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20undergraduates%2C%20applications%20are%20typically%20due%20in%20June%20or%20July%2C%20interviews%20are%20conducted%20in%20August%2C%20and%20offers%20are%20given%20by%20September%20or%20October%20for%20positions%20that%20start%20the%20following%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20undergraduates%20should%20ideally%20figure%20out%20by%20the%20second%20semester%20of%20sophomore%20year%20that%20they%20want%20to%20go%20into%20consulting%2C%20so%20they%20can%20start%20prepping%20and%20applying%20to%20land%20internships%20for%20their%20summer%20after%20junior%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20first-year%20MBAs%20seeking%20internships%2C%20application%20deadlines%20are%20typically%20in%20November%2C%20with%20interviews%20in%20January%2C%20and%20offers%20extended%20by%20the%20end%20of%20January%20for%20positions%20that%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20second-year%20MBAs%20looking%20for%20a%20full-time%20role.%20Application%20deadlines%20are%20in%20August%20and%20September%2C%20followed%20by%20interviews%20and%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMian%20said%20being%20aware%20of%20these%20timelines%20so%20you%20can%20prepare%20and%20network%20well%20in%20advance%20is%20key%20to%20landing%20a%20consulting%20role.%20He%20said%20how%20long%20you've%20prepared%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20number%20one%20determinant%20in%20terms%20of%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20wait%20to%20start%20preparing%20for%20the%20interview%20until%20you%20already%20have%20one%2C%20it's%20almost%20always%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f52bb420-9b6c-40a0-8e1b-de87be2c6420%5C%22%3EFocus%20on%20mastering%20case%20studies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECase%20interviews%20are%20a%20unique%20and%20notoriously%20tough%20part%20of%20getting%20hired%20in%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20case%20interview%2C%20candidates%20are%20presented%20with%20a%20business%20problem%20and%20need%20to%20develop%20a%20plan%20to%20solve%20it%20in%20real%20time.%20Preparing%20for%20case%20interviews%20can%20be%20the%20most%20time-consuming%20part%20of%20getting%20a%20job%20in%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCase%20in