%20surprises%20of%20my%20stay%20was%20catching%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20northern%20lights.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cabin%20at%20night%20in%20front%20of%20mountains%20with%20stars%20and%20purple%20and%20green%20aurora%20lights%20in%20the%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674df1bf9e9761932b4a3035%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20glimpse%20of%20the%20auroras%20at%20Hotel%20Yellowstone.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20I%20took%20a%20peaceful%20walk%20back%20to%20my%20room%2C%20coated%20myself%20in%20a%20thick%20robe%2C%20and%20headed%20to%20the%20balcony.%20I%20expected%20to%20hear%20whispers%20of%20other%20guests%20enjoying%20the%20outdoor%20view%2C%20but%20it%20was%20just%20as%20silent%20and%20peaceful%20as%20when%20I%20first%20stepped%20onto%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitting%20in%20a%20lounge%20chair%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20faint%20flutter%20of%20color%20in%20the%20sky%20and%20immediately%20jumped%20up%20and%20leaned%20on%20the%20railing.%20Purple%20and%20green%20hues%20danced%20so%20subtly%20that%20I%20had%20to%20confirm%20what%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20seeing%20with%20a%20long%20exposure%20on%20my%20camera.%20And%20it%20appears%20that%20I%20was%20right%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20spotted%20the%20northern%20lights%20in%20Wyoming%20of%20all%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20auroras%20has%20been%20on%20my%20bucket%20list%20since%20I%20knew%20the%20phenomenon%20existed.%20And%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20are%20in%20the%20world%2C%20a%20trip%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-saw-northern-lights-free-why-tours-bad-deal-sometimes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esee%20the%20northern%20lights%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20never%20guaranteed.%20So%2C%20I%20certainly%20never%20thought%20I'd%20stumble%20upon%20them%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20hardly%20see%20them%20with%20my%20eyes%20alone%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20that%20if%20the%20environment%20hadn't%20been%20so%20free%20of%20distractions%2C%20I%20might%20have%20missed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20other%20grand%20surprise%20of%20my%20stay%20was%20the%20last%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moose%20sighting%20at%20breakfast.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20moose%20walking%20on%20a%20hillside%20with%20a%20valley%20and%20mountains%20in%20the%20background%20and%20a%20similar%20frame%20of%20the%20same%20moose%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675c691457df667cc5a62986%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20moose%20walks%20across%20the%20adults-only%20resort.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20never%20seen%20a%20moose%20before%20having%20breakfast%20at%20Olivia's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20I%20was%2C%20dining%20at%20a%20table%20against%20the%20back%20window%2C%20when%20a%20moose%20casually%20walked%20along%20the%20property%20just%20outside%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20stunned%2C%20but%20my%20server%20was%20not%20%E2%80%94%20they%20said%20the%20moose%20hangs%20out%20regularly%20and%20is%20often%20seen%20swimming%20in%20the%20pond%20and%20drying%20off%20in%20the%20flower%20beds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20staying%20there%20myself%2C%20I%20could%20see%20why.%20The%20kid-free%20environment%20was%20calm%20and%20quiet.%20I%20imagine%20the%20serene%20nature%20of%20the%20resort%20could%20make%20wildlife%20more%20comfortable%20in%20the%20human%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20the%20adults-only%20element%20was%20key%20to%20having%20these%20surreal%20moments%20with%20nature%20without%20sacrificing%20comfort%20and%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw