0In%20Kuwait%2C%20Meets%20Translator%2C%20Publisher%20Of%20Mahabharata%2C%20Ramayana%20In%20Arabic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Kuwait%2C%20PM%20Modi%20met%20Abdulla%20Al%20Baroun%2C%20who%20translated%20both%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata%20in%20Arabic%2C%20and%20Abdul%20Lateef%20Al%20Nesef%2C%20who%20published%20the%20Arabic%20versions%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20and%20the%20Mahabharata.%20PM%20Modi%20mentioned%20this%20in%20his%20monthly%20radio%20address%20'Mann%20Ki%20Baat'.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20met%20Mangal%20Sain%20Handa%2C%20a%20101-year-old%20retired%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20(IFS)%20officer%20living%20in%20Kuwait.%20The%20retired%20officer%20had%20requested%20on%20social%20media%20that%20he'd%20like%20to%20meet%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BLanded%20in%20Kuwait%20to%20a%20warm%20welcome.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20PM%20in%2043%20years%2C%20and%20it%20will%20undoubtedly%20strengthen%20the%20India-Kuwait%20friendship%20across%20various%20sectors.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20programmes%20scheduled%20for%20later%20today%20and%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20X.%20The%20last%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20to%20visit%20Kuwait%20was%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%201981.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20received%20by%20Sheikh%20Fahad%20Yousef%20Saud%20Al-Sabah%2C%20the%20First%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Minister%20of%20Defence%20and%20Interior%20of%20Kuwait.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20his%20talks%20with%20the%20top%20Kuwaiti%20leadership%20would%20be%20an%20opportunity%20to%20work%20out%20a%20roadmap%20for%20a%20futuristic%20partnership%20between%20India%20and%20Kuwait.%20%26quot%3BWe%20deeply%20value%20the%20historical%20connection%20with%20Kuwait%20that%20has%20been%20nurtured%20over%20generations.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20strong%20trade%20and%20energy%20partners%20but%20also%20have%20shared%20interest%20in%20peace%2C%20security%2C%20stability%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%20West%20Asia%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20his%20meetings%20with%20the%20Emir%2C%20the%20Crown%20Prince%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Kuwait.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20attend%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%2026th%20Arabian%20Gulf%20Cup%20in%20Kuwait.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20is%20among%20the%20top%20trading%20partners%20of%20Kuwait.%20The%20Indian%20community%20is%20the%20largest%20expatriate%20community%20in%20Kuwait.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndians%20form%2021%20per%20cent%20(1%20million)%20of%20the%20total%20population%20of%20Kuwait%20and%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20work-force%20(approximately%209%20lakh).%20Indian%20workers%20top%20the%20private%20sector%20as%20well%20as%20the%20domestic%20sector%20workforce%20list%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Kuwait.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKuwait%20and%20India's%20bilateral%20trade%20was%20valued%20at%20%2410.47%20billion%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202023-24.%20Kuwait%20is%20also%20India's%20sixth-largest%20crude%20supplier%2C%20meeting%203%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20country's%20energy%20needs.%20Indian%20exports%20to%20Kuwait%20reached%20%242%20billion%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20while%20investments%20by%20the%20Kuwait%20Investment%20Authority%20in%20India%20exceed%20%2410%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20and%20Kuwait%20have%20enjoyed%20traditionally%20friendly%20relations%2C%20with%20links%20dating%20back%20to%20pre-oil%20Kuwait%20when%20maritime%20trade%20with%20India%20was%20the%20backbone%20of%20its%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734779040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fp67pj5b_narendra-modi-kuwait_625x300_21_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-in-kuwait-meets-translator-publisher-of-mahabharata-ramayana-in-arabic-10-points-7301042%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20arrived%20in%20Kuwait%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20where%20he%20will%20meet%20the%20Indian%20community%20and%20hold%20talks%20with%20the%20Kuwaiti%20leadership.%20He%20met%20the%20two%20translators%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20and%20the%20Mahabharata%20in%20Arabic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Dies%20After%20Being%20Dragged%20For%2030%20Km%20Under%20UP%20Official's%20Car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThirty%20kilometres.%20A%2035-year-old%20man%20on%20a%20bike%20died%20after%20he%20was%20dragged%20this%20far%20under%20the%20car%20of%20a%20revenue%20official%20(Tehsildar)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20which%20took%20place%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20was%20reported%20from%20Bahraich%2C%20nearly%20127%20km%20from%20state%20capital%20Lucknow.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20identified%20as%20Narendra%20Kumar%20Haldar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Payagpur%2C%20was%20returning%20home%20on%20his%20bike%20when%20the%20accident%20occurred%20on%20the%20Nanpara-Bahraich%20road%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMere%20teen%20bachhe%20hain%20(I%20have%20three%20children)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20distraught%20wife%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20crying%20inconsolably%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20victim's%20body%20got%20entangled%20in%20the%20vehicle%20and%20was%20dragged%20for%20the%20entire%20distance%2C%20reaching%20the%20Nanpara%20Tehsil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaib%20Tehsildar%20Shailesh%20Kumar%20Awasthi%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20present%20in%20the%20vehicle%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20has%20been%20recommended%20for%20suspension%20by%20District%20Magistrate%20Monika%20Rani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20of%20a%20car%20colliding%20with%20a%20bike%20came%20to%20notice.%20The%20Naib%20Tehsildar%20of%20Nanpara%20had%20come%20to%20Bahraich%20in%20the%20Tehsildar's%20car%20for%20some%20work%20and%20was%20returning%20to%20Nanpara.%20It%20has%20been%20learnt%20that%20a%20body%20got%20stuck%20with%20his%20car%20that%20drove%20till%20Nanpara%20Tehsil.%20According%20to%20the%20naib%20tehsildar%2C%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20it.%20A%20recommendation%20has%20been%20made%20to%20suspend%20the%20naib%20tehsildar%20who%20was%20in%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Rani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle's%20driver%2C%20Meraj%20Ahmed%2C%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20confirmed%20that%20the%20body%20was%20dragged%20for%2030%20kilometers%20to%20Nanpara%20when%20the%20locations%20of%20the%20deceased%20Narendra%20Haldar%20and%20the%20tehsildar's%20driver%20Meraj%20Ahmed%20were%20tracked%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident%2C%26quot%3B%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Vrinda%20Shukla%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20negligence%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unlikely%20that%20a%20body%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20vehicle%20for%2030%20kilometers%20and%20no%20one%20came%20to%20know%20about%20it.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20vehicle%20was%20not%20stopped%20due%20to%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20Vrinda%20Shukla%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20said%20that%20an%20investigation%20is%20underway%20to%20determine%20the%20exact%20circumstances%20of%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolice%20are%20examining%20CCTV%20footage%20along%20the%2030-kilometer%20route%20to%20reconstruct%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20police%20complaint%20lodge%20regarding%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20victim%20have%20mentioned%20the%20vehicle%20of%20the%20tehsildar%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Saleem%20Siddiqui)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734778980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F81n9b9n_bahraich-_625x300_21_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-dies-after-being-dragged-for-30-km-under-up-officials-car-7301039%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirty%20kilometres.%20A%2035-year-old%20man%20on%20a%20bike%20died%20after%20he%20was%20dragged%20this%20far%20under%20the%20car%20of%20a%20revenue%20official%20(Tehsildar)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Today's%20Mortgage%20Rates%20%7C%20Rates%20Jumped%20Following%20This%20Week's%20Fed%20Cut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-saturday-21-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fhow-we-evaluate-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMortgage%20rates%20for%20December%2021%2C%202024%2C%20are%20around%