e%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6744ffcffa0140cdd5655bb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20spent%20his%20first%20Christmas%20sober%20by%20himself%20and%20it%20helped%20with%20temptation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20I%20was%20discharged%20after%20an%20eight-day%20admission%20for%20detox%2C%20and%20my%20first%20priority%20was%20getting%20through%20my%20coming%20holiday%20without%20any%20alcohol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7f6391f-0550-4f4a-9da1-9150a64e50eb%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20treated%20the%20day%20like%20a%20normal%20one%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20days%20before%20Christmas%20Day%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20treat%20it%20like%20any%20other%20day%20but%20make%20it%20extra%20special.%20I%20bought%20a%20chicken%20to%20roast%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20an%20extra%20nice%20dessert.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20I%20was%20no%20longer%20drinking%20alcohol%2C%20my%20biggest%20dilemma%20was%20what%20I%20should%20drink.%20So%20I%20bought%20fizzy%20grape%20juice%20%E2%80%94%20like%20wine%20but%20without%20the%20alcohol.%20Every%20time%20I%20felt%20my%20anxieties%20rise%20about%20the%20big%20day%2C%20I%20told%20myself%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20a%20day%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20over%20before%20you%20know%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20surprised%20me%20was%20that%20no%20one%20really%20asked%20me%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20for%20Christmas%2C%20which%20actually%20made%20it%20easier.%20In%20previous%20years%2C%20before%20my%20epic%20relapse%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20my%20friend's%20house.%20His%20mother%20would%20come%20over%20from%20Paris%3B%20he'd%20cook%20pheasant%20and%20all%20the%20trimmings.%20However%2C%20this%20year%2C%20he%20and%20his%20mother%20were%20going%20to%20Switzerland%20for%20a%20skiing%20trip%2C%20leaving%20me%20out%20in%20the%20cold.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20teens%20and%2020s%2C%20I%20would%20go%20to%20my%20dad's%20place%2C%20which%20often%20involved%20him%20being%20drunk%20and%20passing%20out%20in%20the%20afternoon.%20This%20was%20not%20something%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20and%20it%20only%20served%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20why%20I%20needed%20to%20stay%20sober.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b49805d-4363-4e13-88b1-2421e9b758d3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%20can%20be%20anything%20you%20want%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20realized%20that%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bright%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20do%20Christmas.%20That%20was%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20pressure%20came%20from%20%E2%80%94%20the%20traditions%2C%20the%20presents%2C%20the%20goodwill%2C%20and%20the%20expectations%20that%20come%20with%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20big%20day%20itself%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20exactly%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do.%20I'd%20earned%20it%20after%20all%20the%20work%20I'd%20put%20into%20my%20sobriety%20the%20previous%20few%20weeks.%20I%20cooked%20my%20roast%20chicken%20with%20unconventional%20herbs%20and%20spices%20and%20had%20my%20gluten-free%20dessert%20and%20sparkling%20grape%20juice.%20I%20allowed%20myself%20to%20watch%20trash%20TV%2C%20which%20reminded%20me%20why%20I%20never%20habitually%20watched%20anything.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20Christmases%20gone%20by%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20get%20up%20to%20go%20anywhere%20or%20even%20get%20dressed.%20Knowing%20there%20were%20no%20people%20involved%20eased%20my%20anxieties.%20There%20were%20no%20awkward%20conversations%20around%20the%20dinner%20table%20with%20relatives%20I%20only%20see%20at%20Christmas%2C%20big%20birthdays%2C%20or%20funerals.%20Nor%20did%20I%20have%20to%20down%20a%20bottle%20of%20wine%20to%20ensure%20there%20was%20enough%20alcohol%20in%20my%20system%20to%20get%20me%20through%20the%20day.%20This%20was%20my%20Christmas%2C%20and%20I%20did%20it%20my%20way.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20bliss.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20people%20think%20the%20idea%20of%20spending%20Christmas%20on%20their%20own%20sounds%20lonely%20and%20unappealing.%20For%20me%2C%20spending%20Christmas%20alone%20is%20about%20taking%20responsibility.%20The%20alternative%20is%20that%20I%20would%20re-expose%20myself%20to%20triggers%20that%20contributed%20to%20my%20complex%20PTSD%2C%20which%20underpinned%20my%20alcohol%20addiction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20approaching%20my%20sixth%20sober%20solo%20Christmas%2C%20I'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholidays-sobriety-spending-days-alone-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734778022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6744fee89f2901eb6036cd7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholidays-sobriety-spending-days-alone-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20decided%20to%20treat%20Christmas%20Day%20as%20any%20other%20day%20to%20not%20feel%20any%20pressure.%20I%20was%20alone%20in%20my%20apartment%20and%20it%20really%20helped%20me%20get%20through%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sam%20Thomas)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholidays-sobriety-spending-days-alone-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Angelina%E2%80%99s%20looks%20spark%20an%20unhealthy%20social%20media%20trend%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734777755000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116535228%2Cimgsize-1153720.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fangelina