%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20enormous%20plans%20to%20establish%20solar%20and%20wind%20facilities%20and%20have%20large%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fv4lJv6HEgZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fv4lJv6HEgZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IANS%20(%40ians_india)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fians_india%2Fstatus%2F1870397796005954004%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20committed%20%2410%20billion%20investment%20in%20US%20energy%20security%20and%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20aiming%20to%20create%20up%20to%2015%2C000%20local%20jobs%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolheim%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20US%20must%20stop%20such%20an%20authoritative%20approach%20and%20rather%20look%20into%20the%20consequences%20of%20such%20meaningless%20actions%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sure%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%20will%20come%20back%20even%20stronger%20after%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolheim%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Executive%20Director%20of%20the%20UN%20Environment%20Programme%2C%20said%20that%20the%20time%20is%20over%20when%20Western%20nations%20like%20the%20United%20States%20were%20the%20arbitrators%20and%20judges%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20This%20must%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Breon%20Peace%2C%20the%20US%20Attorney%20who%20presented%20charges%20against%20Adani%20Group%20officials%2C%20has%20reportedly%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20step%20down%20on%20January%2010%20-%20just%20days%20away%20from%20Donald%20Trump's%20inauguration%20as%20the%20next%20US%20President%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20DoJ%20indicted%20Adani%20Group%20officials%20on%20allegations%20ranging%20from%20securities%20fraud%20to%20wire%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Group%20vehemently%20rejected%20the%20al