they%20know.%20Chappell%20also%20reflected%20on%20the%20inevitable%20decline%20of%20elite%20batsmen%20and%20how%20it%20manifests%20in%20the%20careers%20of%20modern%20greats%20like%20Kohli%2C%20Smith%2C%20and%20Root.%20Chappell%20examines%20the%20phenomenon%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3BElite%20Performance%20Decline%20Syndrome%26quot%3B%20(EPDS)%2C%20offering%20a%20rare%20glimpse%20into%20the%20mental%20and%20physical%20battles%20faced%20by%20cricketers%20in%20the%20twilight%20of%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChappell%20begins%20by%20observing%20how%20decline%2C%20while%20gradual%2C%20is%20unmistakable.%20Even%20the%20best%20players%E2%80%94those%20who%20once%20dominated%20with%20flair%20and%20certainty%E2%80%94start%20to%20show%20signs%20of%20hesitation.%20%26quot%3BFor%20players%20like%20Kohli%2C%20Smith%2C%20and%20Root%2C%20the%20decline%20isn't%20dramatic%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20wrote%20in%20an%20opinion%20piece%20for%20The%20Sydney%20Morning%20Herald.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20subtle%E2%80%94a%20shift%20in%20approach%2C%20a%20caution%20that%20replaces%20the%20instinctive%20dominance%20of%20their%20prime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Kohli%2C%20Smith%2C%20and%20Root%2C%20the%20end%20will%20come%E2%80%94not%20when%20others%20tell%20them%2C%20but%20when%20they%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20writes.%20%26quot%3BThe%20battle%20against%20time%20is%20not%20about%20winning%3B%20it's%20about%20finishing%20with%20dignity%2C%20on%20their%20own%20terms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%2C%20who%20once%20intimidated%20bowlers%20with%20his%20commanding%20starts%2C%20has%20begun%20to%20exhibit%20a%20cautious%20approach.%20%26quot%3BHe%20now%20builds%20his%20innings%20differently%2C%20often%20needing%2020%20or%2030%20runs%20to%20regain%20the%20fluency%20that%20once%20came%20naturally%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hesitancy%2C%20Chappell%20argueed%2C%20is%20emblematic%20of%20EPDS.%20Kohli's%20instinctive%20aggression%2C%20tempered%20by%20the%20weight%20of%20expectations%20and%20the%20fear%20of%20failure%2C%20has%20made%20him%20more%20risk-averse.%20%26quot%3BConfidence%20is%20everything%20for%20an%20elite%20athlete%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20writes.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20doubt%20creeps%20in%2C%20it%20disrupts%20the%20clarity%20required%20to%20dominate.%20Kohli's%20internal%20battle%20is%20clear%E2%80%94his%20desire%20to%20attack%20versus%20his%20cautious%20approach%20to%20survival.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESteve%20Smith%2C%20known%20for%20his%20unorthodox%20brilliance%20and%20extraordinary%20ability%20to%20grind%20out%20runs%2C%20is%20battling%20a%20different%20facet%20of%20EPDS.%20%26quot%3BSmith's%20decline%20has%20been%20more%20mental%20than%20physical%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intense%20focus%20and%20meticulous%20preparation%20that%20defined%20Smith's%20batting%20are%20harder%20to%20sustain%20as%20time%20goes%20on.%20%26quot%3BFatigue%E2%80%94both%20mental%20and%20physical%E2%80%94is%20a%20silent%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20writes.%20%26quot%3BFor%20Smith%2C%20maintaining%20that%20razor-sharp%20focus%20over%20long%20innings%20has%20become%20increasingly%20challenging.%20The%20weight%20of%20expectations%2C%20from%20fans%20and%20teammates%20alike%2C%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20emotional%20toll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Joe%20Root%2C%20the%20battle%20is%20as%20much%20about%20mindset%20as%20it%20is%20about%20form.%20Root's%20graceful%20stroke%20play%20and%20ability%20to%20adapt%20to%20any%20situation%20have%20remained%20hallmarks%20of%20his%20game.%20However%2C%20Chappell%20notes%20a%20subtle%20shift%20in%20his%20intent.%20%26quot%3BRoot's%20ability%20to%20dominate%20spinners%20and%20pace%20alike%20is%20still%20there%2C%20but%20his%20willingness%20to%20take%20risks%20has%20diminished%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20observes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoot's%20challenge%20lies%20in%20rekindling%20the%20joy%20of%20batting%2C%20something%20that%20often%20fades%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20responsibility.%20%26quot%3BThe%20hardest%20thing%20isn't%20the%20bowler%20at%20the%20other%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20writes.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20silence%20in%20your%20own%20head%20when%20you%20know%20you're%20not%20the%20player%20you%20once%20were.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChappell%20delved%20into%20the%20scientific%20underpinnings%20of%20EPDS%2C%20explaining%20how%20ageing%20impacts%20both%20the%20mind%20and%20body.%20%26quot%3BThese%20changes%20are%20inevitable%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20writes.%20%26quot%3BThe%20challenge%20is%20how%20players%20like%20Kohli%2C%20Smith%2C%20and%20Root%20adapt%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20players%20from%20cricket-mad%20nations%20like%20India%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20England%2C%20the%20pressures%20of%20decline%20are%20magnified%20by%20public%20scrutiny.%20Chappell%20highlighted%20how%20every%20slump%20in%20form%20is%20dissected%20by%20fans%20and%20pundits%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20mental%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20players%20are%20not%20just%20fighting%20their%20own%20battles%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20writes.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20carrying%20the%20weight%20of%20millions%20of%20fans%20who%20demand%20perfection.%26quot%3B%20He%20recalls%20Sunil%20Gavaskar's%20words%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hardest%20part%20of%20batting%20is%20knowing%20you%20aren't%20what%20you%20were.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Chappell%20believed%20that%20great%20players%20find%20ways%20to%20adapt.%20He%20points%20to%20Kohli's%20recent%20performances%2C%20where%20after%20cautious%20starts%2C%20he%20rediscovered%20his%20rhythm%20and%20delivered%20match-winning%20innings.%20Similarly%2C%20Smith's%20ability%20to%20grind%20through%20tough%20conditions%20and%20Root's%20adaptability%20to%20different%20formats%20are%20testaments%20to%20their%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReaching%2020%20or%2030%20runs%20acts%20as%20a%20psychological%20turning%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20writes.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20moment%20where%20the%20rhythm%20of%20their%20younger%20selves%20resurfaces%2C%20reminding%20them%E2%80%94and%20us%E2%80%94why%20they're%20among%20the%20greatest%20of%20all%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChappell%20concluded%20by%20reflecting%20on%20his%20own%20career%20and%20the%20emotional%20struggle%20of%20letting%20go.%20In%20his%20final%20Test%20at%20the%20SCG%2C%20he%20summoned%20the%20mental%20focus%20of%20his%20younger%20self%20to%20score%20a%20century%2C%20a%20fitting%20end%20to%20his%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChappell%20also%20urged%20fans%20to%20celebrate%20these%20players%20not%20just%20for%20their%20peak%20performances%20but%20for%20their%20resilience%20in%20the%20face%20of%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGreatness%20isn't%20just%20about%20what%20they%20achieve%20in%20their%20prime.%20It's%20about%20how%20they%20adapt%2C%20endure%2C%20and%20finish.%20Kohli%2C%20Smith%2C%20and%20Root%20are%20writing%20the%20final%20chapters%20of%20their%20stories%2C%20and%20we%20should%20honour%20their%20courage%20as%20much%20as%20their%20brilliance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734777300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fqjhr5q08_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_17_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fon-virat-kohlis-retirement-timing-indias-most-controversial-coachs-sharp-dignity-verdict-7298948%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Australia%20captain%20Ian%20Chappell%20wrote%20about%20when%20and%20how%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Steve%20Smith%20and%20Joe%20Root%20should%20retire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3