ederal%20prosecutors%20may%20next%20seek%20an%20indictment%20from%20a%20grand%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20federal%20charges%20now%20introduce%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20accused%20--%20Luigi%20Mangione%20--%20being%20sentenced%20to%20death%20once%20he%20is%20found%20guilty%20of%20the%20federal%20murder%20charge.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20state%20charges%20carry%20a%20maximum%20penalty%20of%20life%20in%20prison%2C%20while%20there%20is%20no%20possibility%20of%20parole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20prosecutors%20have%20not%20indicated%20if%20they%20will%20be%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty.%20Ultimately%2C%20this%20decision%20will%20be%20required%20to%20get%20approval%20from%20the%20US%20Attorney%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734768420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0ci10ono_luigi-mangione-reuters_625x300_12_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftarget-is-insurance-notebook-of-unitedhealthcare-ceos-killer-helps-federal-prosecutors-build-their-case-7299369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20writings%20in%20a%20notebook%20found%20in%20Luigi%20Mangione's%20possession%20are%20helping%20investigators%20build%20a%20federal%20case%20against%20the%20alleged%20killer%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20authorities%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftarget-is-insurance-notebook-of-unitedhealthcare-ceos-killer-helps-federal-prosecutors-build-their-case-7299369%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Getting%20Sacked%2C%20Shaw%20Will%20Now%20Lead%20This%20'Mumbai%20Cricket'%20Team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Prithvi%20Shaw%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107533-prithvi-shaw-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrithvi%2