weet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDense%20fog%20outside.%20Kavach%20shows%20the%20signal%20right%20inside%20the%20cab.%20Pilot%20doesn't%20have%20to%20look%20outside%20for%20signal.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcdQJDYNGrk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcdQJDYNGrk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20(%40AshwiniVaishnaw)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshwiniVaishnaw%2Fstatus%2F1870320902350532849%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Kavach%2C'%20a%20homegrown%20Automatic%20Train%20Protection%20(ATP)%20technology%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20address%20challenges%20posed%20by%20unpredictable%20weather%2C%20such%20as%20dense%20fog%2C%20heavy%20rain%20and%20extreme%20temperatures.%20By%20monitoring%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20train%20and%20ensuring%20it%20stays%20within%20safe%20limits%2C%20Kavach%20can%20intervene%20automatically%20if%20the%20pilot%20fails%20to%20take%20corrective%20action%20in%20time.%20This%20automatic%20response%20significantly%20reduces%20the%20chances%20of%20accidents%2C%20especially%20in%20conditions%20where%20visibility%20is%20severely%20compromised.%20The%20system's%20real-time%20signal%20display%20inside%20the%20cab%20ensures%20that%20drivers%20can%20continue%20operations%20safely%2C%20even%20when%20they%20can't%20rely%20on%20external%20cues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach's%20primary%20function%20is%20to%20monitor%20and%20control%20train%20speeds%2C%20stepping%20in%20when%20the%20loco%20pilot%20fails%20to%20respond.%20If%20the%20train%20exceeds%20the%20speed%20limit%20or%20the%20operator%20misses%20a%20critical%20signal%2C%20the%20system%20automatically%20applies%20the%20brakes%20to%20prevent%20potential%20collisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Vaishnaw%20emphasised%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20rolling%20out%20Kavach%20on%20a%20national%20scale%2C%20with%20plans%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmission%20mode%E2%80%9D%20implementation.%20This%20push%20follows%20a%20few%20high-profile%20train%20accidents%2C%20including%20a%20deadly%20collision%20in%20Darjeeling%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20in%20June%202024%2C%20which%20occurred%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20Kavach%20on%20the%20tracks.%20In%20the%20aftermath%2C%20there%20have%20been%20increasing%20calls%20to%20expedite%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20system%2C%20particularly%20in%20areas%20prone%20to%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%20such%20as%20fog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20November%202024%2C%20Kavach%20has%20been%20deployed%20on%20more%20than%201%2C548%20route%20kilometres%20(RKm)%20across%20the%20South%20Central%20Railway%20and%20North%20Central%20Railway%20regions.%20Work%20is%20also%20progressing%20rapidly%20on%20key%20corridors%20such%20as%20Delhi-Mumbai%20and%20Delhi-Howrah%2C%20which%20together%20cover%20around%203%2C000%20RKm.%20Regular%20trials%20are%20being%20conducted%20to%20ensure%20the%20system%20is%20ready%20for%20full%20deployment%20on%20these%20critical%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734762000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Foqk7m5bo_kavach-railway_625x300_21_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frailway-minister-ashwini-vaishnaw-highlights-kavach-s-role-in-preventing-accidents-during-dense-fog-7299325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20has%20highlighted%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Kavach'%20system%20in%20ensuring%20train%20safety%20during%20the%20foggy%20weather.%20Kavach%2C%20which%20means%20armour%2C%20is%20an%20anti-collision%20system%20developed%20to%20achieve%20the%20goal%20of%20%26quot%3Bzero%20accidents.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frailway-minister-ashwini-vaishnaw-highlights-kavach-s-role-in-preventing-accidents-during-dense