Sheshandeep%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20saw%20the%20nameplates%20of%20women%20proudly%20displayed%20on%20every%20door%20in%20the%20village.%20The%20results%20were%20immediate%20and%20impactful.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20one%20young%20woman%20who%20came%20to%20me%2C%20with%20tears%20in%20her%20eyes%2C%20thanking%20me%20for%20this%20initiative.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20never%20been%20allowed%20to%20leave%20her%20home%20or%20make%20decisions%20for%20herself.%20But%20now%2C%20when%20she%20saw%20her%20name%20on%20the%20doorplate%2C%20she%20felt%20proud%20and%20recognised%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheshandeep%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripples%20of%20change%20were%20felt%20across%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20family%2C%20no%20one%20objected%20to%20the%20nameplate.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20my%20name%20is%20recognised%20alongside%20the%20men%E2%80%99s.%20It%20shows%20that%20we%20are%20equal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rani%20Kaur%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20woman%20from%20Manak%20Khana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20see%20my%20name%20on%20the%20doorplate%2C%20I%20feel%20proud.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20a%20name%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20recognition%20of%20who%20I%20am.%20It%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaspreet%20Kaur%2C%20a%20younger%20resident%20of%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20to%20see%20the%20change%20in%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20younger%20generation.%20They%20see%20women%20leading%2C%20and%20they%20aspire%20to%20be%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Bhullar%2C%20who%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20bringing%20to%20life%20the%20initiative%2C%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20but%20it%20made%20a%20huge%20difference.%20For%20generations%2C%20our%20society%20had%20only%20recognised%20men.%20Sheshandeep%E2%80%99s%20vision%20was%20fresh%2C%2