20building%20are%20central%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20The%20enterprise%20has%20partnered%20with%20Assam%20Rifles%20to%20provide%20training%20to%20women%20in%20areas%20affected%20by%20poverty%20and%20insurgency.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20conducts%20workshops%20in%20schools%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(2020)%20skill%20development%20module.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Light%2C%20sturdy%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountry%20boats%20are%20prone%20to%20leaks%20and%20instability%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20fatal%20accidents%20each%20year.%20While%20fibre-glass%20boats%20are%20a%20common%20alternative%2C%20they%20are%20neither%20biodegradable%20nor%20recyclable%2C%20often%20ending%20up%20in%20rivers%20and%20causing%20significant%20environmental%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20founded%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%20in%20Assam%20in%202020.%20His%20startup%20aims%20to%20revolutionise%20inland%20water%20transport%20by%20creating%20safer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337729%2Fbihar-bamboo-startup-entrepreneur-satyam-sundaram-eco-friendly-products-profits%2F%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20composite%20boats%2C%20offering%20sustainable%20water%20mobility%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20innovation%20took%20over%20two%20years%20to%20materialise.%20Our%20boats%20are%20made%20of%2085%20percent%20bamboo%2C%2010%20percent%20polymers%2C%20and%20five%20percent%20fibre-glass.%20The%20main%20advantage%20of%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%20is%20their%20sustainability.%20Bamboo%20is%20six%20times%20more%20sustainable%20than%20hardwood%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20fast-growing%2C%20abundant%2C%20and%20incredibly%20strong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glimpse%20into%20the%20boat-making%20process%20(L)%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20(R)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20glimpse%20into%20the%20boat-making%20process%20(L)%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20(R)%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBamboo%20composite%20boards%20are%20lightweight%2C%20cost-effective%2C%20and%20biodegradable%2C%20with%20an%20expected%20lifespan%20of%2010%20to%2015%20years.%20Their%20compressive%20strength%20and%20flexibility%20also%20provide%20better%20shock%20absorption%20compared%20to%20boats%20made%20from%20other%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20traditional%20wooden%20boats%2C%20which%20require%20trees%20to%20be%20felled%2C%20bamboo%20boats%20leave%20no%20such%20ecological%20footprint.%20Bamboo%20composite%20boats%20also%20have%20the%20lowest%20carbon%20footprint%20of%20any%20boat-making%20process%2C%20claims%20Deka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%20are%2020%20to%2030%20percent%20more%20expensive%20than%20traditional%20wooden%20boats.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20wooden%20canoe%20for%20four%20people%20costs%20Rs%2060%2C000%2C%20while%20our%20boats%20range%20from%20Rs%2090%2C000%20for%20a%20four-person%20canoe%20to%20up%20to%20Rs%208%20lakh%20for%20a%20trimaran.%20However%2C%20our%20boats%20are%20half%20the%20price%20of%20fibre-glass%20boats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20making%20the%20boats%20is%20labour-intensive.%20The%20core%20material%20consists%20of%20compressed%20bamboo%20mat%20boards%2C%20created%20by%20pressing%20layers%20of%20woven%20bamboo%20mats%20together%2C%20which%20are%20then%20joined%20to%20form%20the%20boats.%20Ravi%20has%20also%20innovated%20to%20strengthen%20these%20boards%20and%20make%20them%20waterproof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Deka%20at%20work%20designing%20the%20boats%20(L)%3B%20A%20canoe%20made%20of%20bamboo%20composites%20(R)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388179%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERavi%20Deka%20at%20work%20designing%20the%20boats%20(L)%3B%20A%20canoe%20made%20of%20bamboo%20composites%20(R)%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boats%20are%2040%20to%2060%20percent%20lighter%20than%20their%20fibre-glass%20or%20wooden%20counterparts.%20With%20bamboo%20boats%2C%20you%20can%20achieve%20good%20speeds%20using%20less%20power%2C%20making%20them%20more%20efficient%20and%20lowering%20running%20costs%2C%20he%20further%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20incubated%20at%20IIT%20Guwahati%20and%20has%20developed%20prototypes%20of%20six%20different%20types%20of%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%2C%20with%20patents%20pending.%20The%20smallest%20boat%20is%20a%20three-person%20canoe%2C%20while%20the%20company%20also%20manufactures%20canoes%20with%20outriggers%20%E2%80%94%20structures%20that%20enhance%20stability%20and%20improve%20manoeuvrability.%20The%20largest%20model%20is%20a%20trimaran%2C%20capable%20of%20carrying%2018%20passengers%20and%20two%20crew%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20potential%20applications%20for%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%2C%E2%80%9D%20continues%20Ravi.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20serve%20as%20rescue%20boats%20during%20floods%2C%20transporting%20people%20and%20relief%20materials%2C%20particularly%20drinking%20water.%20They%20are%20ideal%20for%20forest%20patrolling%20in%20shallow%20waters%20and%20marshlands%2C%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20stuck%20in%20the%20mud.%20They%20offer%20an%20affordable%20option%20for%20fishermen%20and%20can%20function%20as%20small%20ferries%20or%20water%20taxis.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20eco-tourism%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20commercial%20production%20has%20yet%20to%20begin%2C%20the%20company%20has%20received%20inquiries%20from%20abroad%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%2